metadata.description:
It is time. 🕛 It is time to post my first on-chain message and let it live inside digital universe forever. 🚀 I have been waiting for this moment for a long time and I am extremely excited to finally be able to start using #authencity. 💯 While this is not a Moon landing I have to say that this is a small step for Authencity but a huge step for me personally. ❤️ Thank you all who are & will contribute to growth of this platform and let us build this amazing decentralized and open platform together with us. 🤗 If you are reading this message in 100000 years I hope you live in a beautiful world with amazing people (or aliens) around you 😁 Let the journey begin! Welcome to Authencity everyone! Welcome to the future of social media and personal identity! 🎉 🙌 🥂
